{"id":94,"name":"Ash-Sharh","nameArabic":"الشرح","transliteration":"Ash-Sharh","type":"meccan","ayahCount":8,"verses":[{"n":1,"text":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","translit":"Alam nashrah laka sadraka","translation":"Did We not expand for you, [O Muhammad], your breast"},{"n":2,"text":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","translit":"WawadaAAna AAanka wizraka","translation":"And We removed from you your burden"},{"n":3,"text":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","translit":"Allathee anqada thahraka","translation":"Which had weighed upon your back"},{"n":4,"text":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","translit":"WarafaAAna laka thikraka","translation":"And raised high for you your repute"},{"n":5,"text":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","translit":"Fainna maAAa alAAusri yusran","translation":"For indeed, with hardship [will be] ease"},{"n":6,"text":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","translit":"Inna maAAa alAAusri yusran","translation":"Indeed, with hardship [will be] ease"},{"n":7,"text":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","translit":"Faitha faraghta fainsab","translation":"So when you have finished [your duties], then stand up [for worship]"},{"n":8,"text":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","translit":"Waila rabbika fairghab","translation":"And to your Lord direct [your] longing"}]}